  ${
    $d J m n u $.  $d X m n u $.  $d Y m n u $.
    tlmconst.1 $e |- X = U. J $.
    $( A constant sequence converges to the constant. $)
    tlmconst $p |- ( ( J e. Top /\ Y e. X ) ->
                                    ( NN X. { Y } ) ( ~~>t ` J ) Y ) $=
      ( vm vu vn ctop wcel wa cn csn cxp ctlm cfv wbr wf cv cuz wral wrex cnei
      w3a wss fconstg snssi fss syl11anc adantl simpr c1 wceq fveq2 raleqdv
      rcla4ev 1nn fvconst2g adantll adantlr ssnei snssg biimpar syldan adantr
      eqeltrd elnnuz sylan2br r19.21aiva sylancr 3jca tlmbr mpbird ) AHIZCBIZJZ
